analysis.description:
XEther.payoutInvestors has external calls inside a loop:
	- isSuccess = investorsAddress[i].send(paymentAmount) (/unique_chucks/6/0xfee1f560e167cd3c55992c356e712d5ee8c33d49.sol#348-349)

XEther.withdrawJackpotBalance (/unique_chucks/6/0xfee1f560e167cd3c55992c356e712d5ee8c33d49.sol#420-432) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- require(bool)(now - lastTransaction > 2419200) (/unique_chucks/6/0xfee1f560e167cd3c55992c356e712d5ee8c33d49.sol#425-426)
